50
0:02:25.26,000 --> 0:02:28,000
means we couldn't fill a small stadium

51
0:02:28.26,000 --> 0:02:3,000
with all the bonobos that are left in the world --

52
0:02:30.26,000 --> 0:02:33,000
and we're not even sure of that to be honest.

53
0:02:34.26,000 --> 0:02:38,000
Yet, in this land of violence and chaos,

54
0:02:38.26,000 --> 0:02:41,000
you can hear hidden laughter

55
0:02:41.26,000 --> 0:02:43,000
swaying the trees.

56
0:02:43.26,000 --> 0:02:46,000
Who are these cousins?

57
0:02:46.26,000 --> 0:02:5,000
