66
0:03:08.26,000 --> 0:03:1,000
Bonobos, like humans,

67
0:03:10.26,000 --> 0:03:12,000
love to play throughout their entire lives.

68
0:03:12.26,000 --> 0:03:14,000
Play is not just child's games.

69
0:03:14.26,000 --> 0:03:16,000
For us and them,

70
0:03:16.26,000 --> 0:03:19,000
play is foundational for bonding relationships

71
0:03:19.26,000 --> 0:03:21,000
and fostering tolerance.

72
0:03:21.26,000 --> 0:03:23,000
