73
0:03:23.26,000 --> 0:03:26,000
and where we learn about the rules of the game.

74
0:03:26.26,000 --> 0:03:28,000
Play increases creativity

75
0:03:28.26,000 --> 0:03:31,000
and resilience,

76
0:03:31.26,000 --> 0:03:34,000
and it's all about the generation of diversity --

77
0:03:34.26,000 --> 0:03:36,000
diversity of interactions,

78
0:03:36.26,000 --> 0:03:38,000
diversity of behaviors,

79
0:03:38.26,000 --> 0:03:41,000
diversity of connections.

80
0:03:41.26,000 --> 0:03:43,000
And when you watch bonobo play,

81
0:03:43.26,000 --> 0:03:46,000
you're seeing the very evolutionary roots

82
0:03:46.26,000 --> 0:03:48,000
of human laughter, dance

83
0:03:48.26,000 --> 0:03:5,000
and ritual.

84
0:03:50.26,000 --> 0:03:52,000
Play is the glue

85
0:03:52.26,000 --> 0:03:54,000
that binds us together.

